<rss version="2.0"><channel><title>GitHub Trending: Zig, This week</title><link>https://github.com/trending/zig?since=weekly</link><description>The top repositories on GitHub for zig, measured weekly</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2020 01:08:20 GMT</pubDate><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2020 01:08:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>PyRSS2Gen-1.1.0</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><ttl>720</ttl><item><title>ziglang/zig #1 in Zig, This week</title><link>https://github.com/ziglang/zig</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;General-purpose programming language and toolchain for maintaining robust, optimal, and reusable software.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id="readme" class="md" data-path="README.md"&gt;&lt;article class="markdown-body entry-content p-5" itemprop="text"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b0764c677211c6f01f50c047aaf5fc8f094baa7a/68747470733a2f2f7a69676c616e672e6f72672f7a69672d6c6f676f2e737667"&gt;&lt;img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b0764c677211c6f01f50c047aaf5fc8f094baa7a/68747470733a2f2f7a69676c616e672e6f72672f7a69672d6c6f676f2e737667" alt="ZIG" data-canonical-src="https://ziglang.org/zig-logo.svg" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A general-purpose programming language and toolchain for maintaining
&lt;strong&gt;robust&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;optimal&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;reusable&lt;/strong&gt; software.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-resources" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#resources"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Resources&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://ziglang.org/#Introduction" rel="nofollow"&gt;Introduction&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://ziglang.org/download" rel="nofollow"&gt;Download &amp;amp; Documentation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/ziglang/zig/wiki/Community"&gt;Community&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/ziglang/zig/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md"&gt;Contributing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/ziglang/zig/wiki/FAQ"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/ziglang/zig/wiki/Community-Projects"&gt;Community Projects&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-building-from-source" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#building-from-source"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Building from Source&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://dev.azure.com/ziglang/zig/_build/latest?definitionId=1&amp;amp;branchName=master" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/e9f6d052d4322788986723ade734b09d56144866/68747470733a2f2f6465762e617a7572652e636f6d2f7a69676c616e672f7a69672f5f617069732f6275696c642f7374617475732f7a69676c616e672e7a69673f6272616e63684e616d653d6d6173746572" alt="Build Status" data-canonical-src="https://dev.azure.com/ziglang/zig/_apis/build/status/ziglang.zig?branchName=master" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that you can
&lt;a href="https://ziglang.org/download/#release-master" rel="nofollow"&gt;download a binary of master branch&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-stage-1-build-zig-from-c-source-code" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#stage-1-build-zig-from-c-source-code"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Stage 1: Build Zig from C++ Source Code&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-dependencies" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#dependencies"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Dependencies&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-posix" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#posix"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;POSIX&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;cmake &amp;gt;= 2.8.5&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;gcc &amp;gt;= 5.0.0 or clang &amp;gt;= 3.6.0&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;LLVM, Clang, LLD development libraries == 9.x, compiled with the same gcc or clang version above
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use the system package manager, or &lt;a href="https://github.com/ziglang/zig/wiki/How-to-build-LLVM,-libclang,-and-liblld-from-source#posix"&gt;build from source&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-windows" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#windows"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Windows&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;cmake &amp;gt;= 3.15.3&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Microsoft Visual Studio. Supported versions:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2015 (version 14)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2017 (version 15.8)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2019 (version 16)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;LLVM, Clang, LLD development libraries == 9.x
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use the &lt;a href="https://github.com/ziglang/zig/wiki/Building-Zig-on-Windows"&gt;pre-built binaries&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="https://github.com/ziglang/zig/wiki/How-to-build-LLVM,-libclang,-and-liblld-from-source#windows"&gt;build from source&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-instructions" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#instructions"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Instructions&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-posix-1" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#posix-1"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;POSIX&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make install
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-macos" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#macos"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;MacOS&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;brew install cmake llvm@9
brew outdated llvm@9 || brew upgrade llvm@9
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=$(brew --prefix llvm)
make install
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-windows-1" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#windows-1"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Windows&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href="https://github.com/ziglang/zig/wiki/Building-Zig-on-Windows"&gt;https://github.com/ziglang/zig/wiki/Building-Zig-on-Windows&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-stage-2-build-self-hosted-zig-from-zig-source-code" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#stage-2-build-self-hosted-zig-from-zig-source-code"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Stage 2: Build Self-Hosted Zig from Zig Source Code&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note: Stage 2 compiler is not complete. Beta users of Zig should use the
Stage 1 compiler for now.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dependencies are the same as Stage 1, except now you can use stage 1 to compile
Zig code.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;bin/zig build --prefix $(pwd)/stage2
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This produces &lt;code&gt;./stage2/bin/zig&lt;/code&gt; which can be used for testing and development.
Once it is feature complete, it will be used to build stage 3 - the final compiler
binary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-stage-3-rebuild-self-hosted-zig-using-the-self-hosted-compiler" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#stage-3-rebuild-self-hosted-zig-using-the-self-hosted-compiler"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Stage 3: Rebuild Self-Hosted Zig Using the Self-Hosted Compiler&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note: Stage 2 compiler is not yet able to build Stage 3. Building Stage 3 is
not yet supported.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once the self-hosted compiler can build itself, this will be the actual
compiler binary that we will install to the system. Until then, users should
use stage 1.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-debug--development-build" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#debug--development-build"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Debug / Development Build&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;./stage2/bin/zig build --prefix $(pwd)/stage3
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;a id="user-content-release--install-build" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#release--install-build"&gt;&lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Release / Install Build&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;./stage2/bin/zig build install -Drelease
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/article&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><author>ziglang</author><guid isPermaLink="false">https://github.com/ziglang/zig</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2020 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>